    <item>
      <title>大风持续，洛杉矶火灾形势不容乐观</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/los-angeles-faces-little-relief-from-wildfires-as-winds-persist</link>
      <description><![CDATA[干燥炎热的风将在周中加剧洛杉矶的山火 — — 一些预测显示，一月份剩余时间的阵风不会有太大缓解 — — 南加州正面临着今年山火最严重的开端之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/los-angeles-faces-little-relief-from-wildfires-as-winds-persist</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 14:12:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃塞俄比亚开设证券交易所，仅一家上市且无经纪人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/ethiopia-opens-stock-exchange-with-one-listing-and-no-brokers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃塞俄比亚开设了证券交易所 — 这是吸引投资者进入刚从内战中复苏的经济体的计划的一部分 — 没有任何经纪人，也不需要首次公开募股。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/ethiopia-opens-stock-exchange-with-one-listing-and-no-brokers</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 15:08:22 GMT</pubDate>
